ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs (NTFS read-write filesystem driver)
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs:
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: The NTFS-3G driver is an open source, freely available NTFS driver
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: for Linux with read and write support.  It provides safe and fast
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: handling of the Windows XP, Windows Server 2003, Windows 2000 and
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: Windows Vista file systems.  Most POSIX file system operations are
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: supported, with the exception of full file ownership and access
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: rights support.
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs:
ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs: http://www.tuxera.com/community/open-source-ntfs-3g_ntfsprogs/
